\begin_layout Standard
There are 4 types of financial statements: balance sheet, income statement,
 shareholder's statement of equity, cash flow statement.
 Each company is obligated once a year to submit an annual report, which
 is usually a very long & bulky document.
 It containt the 4 financial statements (they are small segments in it).
\end_layout

